36#include "mech_locl.h"
37
38
39GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
40gss_release_oid(OM_uint32 *minor_status, gss_OID *oid)
41{
42 gss_OID o = *oid;
43
44 *oid = GSS_C_NO_OID;
45
46 if (minor_status != NULL)
47 *minor_status = 0;
48
49 if (o == GSS_C_NO_OID)
50 return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
51
52 if (o->elements != NULL) {
53 free(o->elements);
54 o->elements = NULL;
55 }
56 o->length = 0;
57 free(o);
58
59 return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
60}
